                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00 Tsinan/5: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-05-03T17:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 3, 1928—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>144. Your 303, May 3, 6 p.m.<note n="39" xml:id="d153fn39">Not printed.</note>
                    Can you ascertain and inform Department by telegram present situation with
                    regard to American Consul and other Americans at Tsinan?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
